ir mother.\n\nIn Little Dragons Caf\u00e9, players can choose to play as either sibling Ren or Rin. The story-driven gameplay features a balance of three elements:\n\nManage your caf\u00e9 - Run your own caf\u00e9 by preparing tasty dishes, serving your customers, and managing a colorful cast of eccentric staff and visitors.\n\nExplore the world - Discover an entirely new world filled with wildlife, secrets, and dangers while collecting ingredients and recipes to enhance your caf\u00e9 menu.\n\nRaise a Dragon - Care for and train your very own dragon as he grows from baby to adult. Explore, hunt, and uncover new areas with your faithful companion.", "themes": [{"id": 28, "name": "Business"}, {"id": 33, "name": "Sandbox"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/little-dragons-cafe", "videos": [{"id": 18911, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "pc8V0dQMaLc", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pc8V0dQMaLc", "title": "Little Dragons Caf\u00e9", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pc8V0dQMaLc/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 23019, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "Xivi9o9NCbM", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xivi9o9NCbM", "title": "Little Dragons Caf\u00e9 - Explore a massive world", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Xivi9o9NCbM/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}